Install NixOS
    $ git clone <repo>
    $ cd Dandelions
    $ git checkout excludes-nixy
    $ sudo nixos-generate-config --no-filesystems --show-hardware-config > ./hardware.nix
    $ vim ./modules/disko.nix
    $ sudo nix-shell -p disko --run "disko -m destroy,format,mount ./modules/disko.nix"
    $ sudo nixos-install --flake .#NixOS
    $ reboot

If the Failed to start Import ZFS pool, boot with the zfs_force=1 option as a kernel parameter. You should only need to do this once.
